snippet.title: Let's play Sting [1] - A game literally noone knows!
snippet.description:
Soo, starting a new LP, and this time... actually intending to finish it!
Insanity!

Anyways, this is a game I've often played and enjoyed in my childhood, called Sting. It's apparently made by some company called "O.S.C. inc" which I just can't seem to find any information about on the internet. Neither can I find anything about the game, so I'm pretty sure it's a rare kind of thing.
Actually, it feels kinda nice to - for once - be the first one to LP a game for the internet.
I'll see if I can get more background information on this and the company that made it, but for now, enjoy the video!
